kadhal sadugudu is a 2003 tamil family drama film written and directed by durai , starring vikram , priyanka trivedi and prakash raj in the leading roles . the film released in april 2003 to poor reviews and became a box office flop . a telugu dubbed version titled sivudu released in 2004 , which too failed to become a success . later on , the film was also dubbed and released in hindi under the title aparichit 2 on 20 may 2014 , and met with the similar response .